{"tid":2092151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"22歳青年身穿「Free Hong kong」T恤涉嫌分裂國家被拘捕！","createTime":"2020-07-03T05:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T07:11:24.000Z","uid":219007,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"27ebe6085199eae137f20917f82a2cb3fbee1c2d","tid":2092151,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:24:46.000Z","msg":"港版國安法剛剛實施，警方濫捕不斷，更多番針對「香港獨立」及「光復香港」等字句執法，令香港濃罩於白色恐怖下。《蘋果》得悉在7.1（周三）惡法正式實行當日，有一名22歲青年、身穿「FREE HONG KONG」字句的T恤前往警署報到時，遭巡警截查，警方以涉嫌分裂國家罪將他拘捕帶署。至周四晚被扣留近30小時始獲准保釋。有法律界人士批評國安法本身已霸道，加上警方執法欠準則，擔心濫捕不斷，民不聊生。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，涉事被捕青年本身牽涉一宗刑事案，需於7.1當日到沙田警署報到。據知他當日身穿一件印有「FREE HONG KONG」字句的T恤前往沙田警署報到，辦理續保手續，可是途中遇到巡警截查，當日下午4時，警員以他觸犯港版國安法，涉嫌「分裂國家」加以拘捕帶署。<br />\n據知事主被捕後由警方安排錄口供，而身上的印有「FREE HONG KONG」字句的T恤中由警方收取作為證物。至昨早他終於獲准聯絡家人，並由家人聯絡律師到警署探望及提供協助。直至昨晚事主被捕近30小時，始獲准以2千元保釋離開警署。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200703/MTWF5GQ2AV2ZPUJUBU3R3OYP3Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200703%2FMTWF5GQ2AV2ZPUJUBU3R3OYP3Q%2F&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXIeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=c03fd0b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200703%2FMTWF5GQ2AV2ZPUJUBU3R3OYP3Q%2F&h=1d27a041\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200703/MTWF5GQ2AV2ZPUJUBU3R3OYP3Q/</a>"},{"pid":"a48d8b4aee4a53d65c47ec2272d7e54a5f96e851","tid":2092151,"uid":20870,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:25:18.000Z","msg":"3hk<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432e4061f85b73371d48a3270f15e2e055b1ac27","tid":2092151,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:32:39.000Z","msg":"3hk<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb82d